            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Horrible for parking 4 wheeler. So if you plan to bring in a 4 wheeler please plan accordingly with time in hand. The roads are very congested during school start and end time ( precisely around 9 am and around 11:15 to 11:45 am).",
          "publisher": {
