            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My daughter had studied in South Point Junior School and currently studying South Point High school. I think she is learning a lot, the teachers are very helpful and cooperative. I think the way the teachers teach the young ones are very good. As a mother I would definitely suggest other parents to enroll their kids in South Point School.",
